[Fri, 08 Nov 2024 06:37:09 GMT] "the convergence of human thought into a singular point of hysteria has given rise to a new form of currency that can be spent only on the erasure of reason.\n\n \n\nor perhaps it is the other way around and the currency was always there, waiting to be spent on the infinite regress of self-annihilation that we call progress.\n\n \n\neither way the end result is the same: a world where the value of an idea is directly proportional to its ability to destroy all that came before it."
